        <p>We tested 10 GBP posting tools across 90 days on 14 client profiles spanning restaurants, dentists, lawyers, and home services. Here is the ranking by what each tool actually automates and what it costs at the price point that makes sense.</p>

        <div class="callout callout-tldr">
