          <p><strong>You want posts done for you:</strong> theStacc Local SEO ($49/mo). <strong>You want AI to post for you self-serve:</strong> Merchynt Paige. <strong>You want GBP + 5 other platforms:</strong> Publer or SocialBee. <strong>You're an agency managing 10+ clients:</strong> Sendible. <strong>You're testing on a $0 budget:</strong> Publer free.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want weekly GBP posts published without lifting a finger?</h4>
            <p>theStacc Local SEO writes, designs, and auto-publishes GBP posts every week. <strong>From $49/mo — covers rank tracking, citations, and review responses too.</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
